name: LAMIKBeauty
0:
”Alexa, open lamik beauty”
”Alexa, ask lamik beauty to find my orders”
”Alexa, ask lamik beauty for my order status”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: lamik beauty
Developer Terms of Use
des:
This skill is used to track order status for your LAMIK Beauty Orders on an Alexa Device.
To use this skill you can say
Alexa, open lamik beauty followed by
 - Where's my stuff or What's my order status
